    "updated_at": "2023-11-09T19:52:47Z",
    "body": "If more people have this issue, leave a comment and I'll be happy to reopen, but I concur that this does not appear to be a starship issue at the moment, especially since we don't interact with bash-preexec outside of checking to see that the hooks exist.",
